content: velvet-shark: Merged two PRs this month: #1973 "chore: Cleaner logs on agent startup" and #1705 "Update git command for checking latest release", with substantial code changes totaling +53,059/-44,887 lines across 1,363 files. Activity was sporadic, being active on only 6 out of 31 days. Contributions were primarily focused on other work (71%) with some refactoring and test improvements (14% each), touching both code (67%) and documentation (33%).
